1. signup -as it is
2. create context in app, 
	define userInfo, isLoggedIn state,
		and provide to all routes
3. login - 
	we get token, store token in session storage
		update the userInfo, isLoggedIn states.
			also delete data stored in any previous state
4. logout -
	clear the userInfo, isLoggedIn, any previous state data









